SUMMARY:Challenging Ride (A) - Sunday Worlds (32R)
DESCRIPTION:Lancaster Bicycle Club (LBC) Meetup\nAnticipated average pace:
  **18-20 mph**\n\nCue and GPX link: [https://ridewithgps.com/routes/451802
 82](https://ridewithgps.com/routes/45180282)\n\nThis ride has been a class
 ic in Lancaster County for a long time. The route is unique in that it sta
 rts and finishes at two different locations. As a result\, most cyclists r
 ide to the start and then ride home from the finish.\n\nIt starts at the M
 illersville Mart: 473 N George St\, Millersville\, PA 17551 (pictured) and
  the finish is at the new Bierhall Brewing Company: 1703 New Holland Pike\
 , Lancaster\, PA 17601. The Bierhall is open for lunch\, so riders are wel
 come to stop in after the ride.\n\n**This is a Challenging (A) level ride 
 and intended to be a NO DROP RIDE.** The ride leader will ride at the adve
 rtised average speed and will do his/her best to keep the group together w
 ith regroupings and a sweeper may also be appointed at the start. **Please
  do not join this ride if you are not willing to stick with the group.** I
 f maintaining an 18-20mph average is beyond your current ability level\, p
 lease consider joining an "Advanced" ride first.\n\nHelmets are mandatory.
  No earbuds. Please bring water and a basic repair kit (spare tube\, tire 
 levers\, pump/CO2 inflator).\n\nTo eliminate passing around a pen and pape
 r waiver\, we require an LBC Club membership and Meetup RSVP below to join
  this ride.\n\nBeing on Meetup does not mean you are a club member. [Join 
 here](https://www.lancasterbikeclub.net/content.aspx?page_id=60&club_id=25
 7148).\n\nYour RSVP is your agreement to abide by the club's [Code of Cond
 uct](https://lancbikeclub.clubexpress.com/content.aspx?page_id=22&club_id=
 257148&module_id=323984)\,\n\n[Rules of the Road](https://lancbikeclub.clu
 bexpress.com/content.aspx?page_id=22&club_id=257148&module_id=325159)\, an
 d [Ride Waiver](https://lancasterbikeclub.net/docs.ashx?id=454318)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/lancaster-bicycle-club/events/3139116
 48/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260323T153324Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260323T153324Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
